  .answer
    %p
      All tickets are on sale from BATS Theatre, and the public can book
      individual tickets for $18/$15, book groups of 6 tickets for $14 each, or
      book a three show pass for $39/30. They get to watch us do amazing improv
      and admire us from afar. If someone asks about it from an audience
      perspective, send them to
